{"id":12224,"name":"Silkworm","slug":"silkworm","url":"https:\/\/www.igdb.com\/games\/silkworm","created_at":1441275806541,"updated_at":1517270714571,"summary":"Silkworm is a classic horizontally-scrolling shoot-em-up. The main difference between this game and many other side-scrolling shoot-em-ups is that you will be on land as well as in the air. The first player would play as a helicopter, but if a second player joins the game, they would play as a jeep. Both players would have to protect each other as well as themselves. After a certain number of kills, a \"goose\" helicopter would form on the screen. If the players managed to destroy it they would get a weapon's powerup. This would go on throughout the entire game, and a \"goose\" could appear even during the fight with the end-of-level baddie.","collection":2926,"rating":79.823110884019,"popularity":1.333333333333333,"total_rating":79.823110884019,"total_rating_count":4,"rating_count":4,"games":[68287,28751,28029,36950,18088,27314,74161,11171,142,27523],"tags":[1,18,268435461,268435489,536870913,536870933,536871510,536871707,536871937,536871971,536872651,536872733,536873753,536874398,536874745,536875056,536875122,536875171,536877820,536879693,536883347,1073741828],"developers":[4453],"publishers":[4719,12390,4453],"category":0,"player_perspectives":[4],"game_modes":[1,2,3],"keywords":[1,21,598,795,1025,1059,1739,1821,2841,3486,3833,4144,4210,4259,6908,8781,12435],"themes":[1,18],"genres":[5,33],"first_release_date":599529600000,"platforms":[52,63,16,15,26,25,18],"release_dates":[{"category":2,"platform":26,"date":631065600000,"region":1,"human":"1989","y":1989,"m":12},{"category":0,"platform":18,"date":644198400000,"region":2,"human":"1990-Jun-01","y":1990,"m":6},{"category":2,"platform":15,"date":631065600000,"region":1,"human":"1989","y":1989,"m":12},{"category":2,"platform":63,"date":631065600000,"region":1,"human":"1989","y":1989,"m":12},{"category":2,"platform":25,"date":599529600000,"region":1,"human":"1